<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-50 to-red-50 rounded-lg shadow-lg" data-controller="exercise-checker">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <!-- Info Box -->
  <div class="mb-6 md:mb-8 bg-yellow-50 border-4 border-yellow-400 rounded-lg p-4 md:p-6">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-pink-600 mb-3">È possibile dividere:</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg list-disc list-inside">
      <li>la vocale iniziale di parola, seguita da consonante (<strong>i-so-la</strong>);</li>
      <li>le consonanti doppie (<strong>pat-ti-ni</strong>);</li>
      <li>il gruppo cq (<strong>ac-qua</strong>);</li>
      <li>l, r, m, n dalla consonante che le segue (<strong>el-mo, por-ta</strong>).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-pink-600 mb-3 mt-4">Non è possibile dividere:</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg list-disc list-inside">
      <li>la lettera s dalla consonante che la segue (<strong>po-sti-no</strong>);</li>
      <li>gl, ch, gh, gli, sc, gn (<strong>fi-glio, chia-ro, ghi-ro</strong>).</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="text-base md:text-lg mt-4 text-pink-700 font-bold">
      Se ci sono due o tre vocali vicine nella stessa parola, ricorda che quasi sempre stanno insieme. Se hai dubbi, consulta il dizionario.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 1: IMPARARE TUTTI - Divide words into syllables -->
  <div class="mb-6 md:mb-8 bg-white rounded-lg p-4 md:p-6 shadow-md">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-pink-600 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-pink-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">1</span>
      <span class="bg-yellow-400 text-blue-800 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm md:text-base font-bold">IMPARARE TUTTI</span>
      Dividi in sillabe le parole di ogni gruppo. Osserva gli esempi.
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6" data-controller="fill-blanks">
      <!-- Group 1 -->
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-300 rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-32">• cassetto</span>
            <span class="text-gray-500">cas/set/to</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-32">• passaggio</span>
            <input type="text"
                   class="border-b-2 border-pink-500 bg-white w-32 md:w-40 px-2 text-right focus:outline-none focus:border-pink-700"
                   data-fill-blanks-target="input"
                   data-answer="pas/sag/gio"
                   data-correct-answer="pas/sag/gio">
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-32">• acquazzone</span>
            <input type="text"
                   class="border-b-2 border-pink-500 bg-white w-36 md:w-44 px-2 text-right focus:outline-none focus:border-pink-700"
                   data-fill-blanks-target="input"
                   data-answer="ac/quaz/zo/ne"
                   data-correct-answer="ac/quaz/zo/ne">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Group 2 -->
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-300 rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-32">• costola</span>
            <span class="text-gray-500">co/sto/la</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-32">• palestra</span>
            <input type="text"
                   class="border-b-2 border-pink-500 bg-white w-32 md:w-40 px-2 text-right focus:outline-none focus:border-pink-700"
                   data-fill-blanks-target="input"
                   data-answer="pa/le/stra"
                   data-correct-answer="pa/le/stra">
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-32">• maschera</span>
            <input type="text"
                   class="border-b-2 border-pink-500 bg-white w-32 md:w-40 px-2 text-right focus:outline-none focus:border-pink-700"
                   data-fill-blanks-target="input"
                   data-answer="ma/sche/ra"
                   data-correct-answer="ma/sche/ra">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Group 3 -->
      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-300 rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-32">• calcoli</span>
            <span class="text-gray-500">cal/co/li</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-32">• pentola</span>
            <input type="text"
                   class="border-b-2 border-pink-500 bg-white w-32 md:w-40 px-2 text-right focus:outline-none focus:border-pink-700"
                   data-fill-blanks-target="input"
                   data-answer="pen/to/la"
                   data-correct-answer="pen/to/la">
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-32">• cartina</span>
            <input type="text"
                   class="border-b-2 border-pink-500 bg-white w-32 md:w-40 px-2 text-right focus:outline-none focus:border-pink-700"
                   data-fill-blanks-target="input"
                   data-answer="car/ti/na"
                   data-correct-answer="car/ti/na">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Group 4 -->
      <div class="bg-orange-50 border-2 border-orange-300 rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-32">• coprire</span>
            <span class="text-gray-500">co/pri/re</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-32">• metrico</span>
