        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 2: Indicate break points -->
  <div class="mb-6 md:mb-8 bg-white rounded-lg p-4 md:p-6 shadow-md">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-pink-600 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-pink-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">2</span>
      Quando spezzi una parola per andare a capo devi considerare la divisione in sillabe. Per ogni parola, indica almeno due punti in cui potresti spezzarla. Osserva l'esempio.
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4" data-controller="fill-blanks">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-base md:text-lg">
        <span class="w-32 font-bold">• pasticcio</span>
        <span class="text-gray-500 flex-1">pa/sticcio - pastic/cio</span>
      </div>

      <% words = [
        {word: 'cocomero', answer: 'co/comero - coco/mero'},
        {word: 'pantofole', answer: 'pan/tofole - panto/fole'},
        {word: 'panettone', answer: 'pa/nettone - panet/tone'},
        {word: 'chimica', answer: 'chi/mica'},
        {word: 'moscerino', answer: 'mo/scerino - mosce/rino'},
        {word: 'ruscello', answer: 'ru/scello - rusce/llo'},
        {word: 'scomparire', answer: 'scom/parire - scompa/rire'},
        {word: 'bollente', answer: 'bol/lente - bollen/te'},
        {word: 'larghezza', answer: 'lar/ghezza - larghe/zza'}
      ] %>

      <% words.each do |item| %>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-base md:text-lg">
          <span class="w-32 font-bold">• <%= item[:word] %></span>
          <input type="text"
                 class="border-b-2 border-pink-500 bg-white w-48 md:w-56 px-2 text-right focus:outline-none focus:border-pink-700"
                 data-fill-blanks-target="input"
                 data-answer="<%= item[:answer] %>"
                 data-correct-answer="<%= item[:answer] %>">
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise Controls -->
  <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls', color: 'pink', current_page: 'nvl5_gr_p012' %>
</div>
